Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.23,1:28:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll greet and hug you all. And try to answer every individual question.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.23,1:28:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But we'll all share it together. Okay? Will that be an alright thing to do?
